TY  - JOUR
T1  - Erratum—A Contract and Balancing Mechanism for Sharing Capacity in a Communication Network
AU  - Anderson, Edward
AU  - Kelly, Frank
AU  - Steinberg, Richard
AU  - Waters, Robert
Y1  - 2007/06/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1060.0663
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.1060.0663
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 1029
EP  - 1031
VL  - 53
IS  - 6
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - In a recent paper, the first three authors proposed a method for determining how much to charge users of a communication network when they share bandwidth, and studied the existence and form of Nash equilibria for players? choices of capacity. However, the proof of one of the propositions in that paper contained a flaw. In this note, we prove that the original proposition is true under an additional condition, and provide two examples to show that this condition is necessary.
AB  - In a recent paper, the first three authors proposed a method for determining how much to charge users of a communication network when they share bandwidth, and studied the existence and form of Nash equilibria for players? choices of capacity. However, the proof of one of the propositions in that paper contained a flaw. In this note, we prove that the original proposition is true under an additional condition, and provide two examples to show that this condition is necessary.
